---
title: Teriyaki-Glazed Chicken & Sesame Fries with Garlic Aioli & Apple Salad
description: When teriyaki sauce and a hot pan collide, you get these deliciously caramelised chicken. Serve them with a
refreshing carrot and apple salad, plus the addition of sesame fries, perfect for soaking up any extra glaze!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
